high_descs: turn left, walk straight through kitchen, stop at counter top with coffee maker on top
open bottom cabinet door on the left, pick up ladle with aqua handle, close cabinet door
turn left, walk straight to stove top, turn right at stove top, stop and face stove top
place ladle inside frying pan on top of stove top
pick up frying pan on top of stove top
turn right, walk to kitchen sink, stop in front of sink
put frying pan into sink basin
anns.task_desc: get ladle and frying pan, put both into kitchen sink basin

high_descs: Move to the counter to the left of the sink
Open the cabinet and pick up the scoop and close the door to the cabinet
Move to the stove to the left of you
Place the scoop in the pan on the stove
Pick up the pan from the stove
Move to the sink to the right of the stove
Place the pan inside of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a scoop in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the wall, the turn right and walk across the room to the kitchen counter.
Open the leftmost cabinet door under the counter in front of you and remove the golden spoon with a blue handle, then close the door.
Turn around and begin walking across the room,  turn right at the stove and walk up to it.
Put the golden spoon in the metal pan that is on the stove.
Pick up the metal pan with the golden spoon in it.
Turn around and walk over to the island, then turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn right and walk up to the sink.
Put the pan with the golden spoon in it into the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a golden spoon in it in the sink.
